name: ROOM#4
description:
Behind the bright colors some devilry is hiding. What is that flying balloon? Why is walking through that door so scary?
Or aren't you scared? Then you're the brave one...

Well, let's see if you have the courage to own this room. 

Personally, I almost ran out of brains while I was making it. 
I kept getting distracted by things, my computer kept crashing, the electricity  swithced  off, light bulbs exploded, and even the cat was acting crazy, screaming and running. 

There's a lot of hidden devilry in my works.Don't let the colors fool you.

2000x2000 animation
